Tails got an idea.
She jumped out of Goldeneye's hands and landed on the
ground, squeaking.
She ran to a tree under which several nuts were
scattered, and started 'collecting' them and putting
them in her squirrel cheek pouches.
Hopefully she could convince them she was just a
larger-then-average squirrel, Goldeneye's pet.
